PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of JAMIE MUIR of Truro, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Caroline Granger.
